{"snp4.12:0.1":"Sutta Nipata 4.12 ","snp4.12:0.2":"Culabyuhasutta ","snp4.12:1.1":"“Sakamsakamditthiparibbasana, ","snp4.12:1.2":"Viggayha nana kusala vadanti; ","snp4.12:1.3":"Yo evam janati sa vedi dhammam, ","snp4.12:1.4":"Idam patikkosamakevali so. ","snp4.12:2.1":"Evampi viggayha vivadayanti, ","snp4.12:2.2":"Balo paro akkusaloti cahu; ","snp4.12:2.3":"Sacco nu vado katamo imesam, ","snp4.12:2.4":"Sabbeva hime kusalavadana”. ","snp4.12:3.1":"“Parassa ce dhammamananujanam, ","snp4.12:3.2":"Balomako hoti nihinapanno; ","snp4.12:3.3":"Sabbeva bala sunihinapanna, ","snp4.12:3.4":"Sabbevime ditthiparibbasana. ","snp4.12:4.1":"Sanditthiya ceva na vivadata, ","snp4.12:4.2":"Samsuddhapanna kusala mutima; ","snp4.12:4.3":"Na tesam koci parihinapanno, ","snp4.12:4.4":"Ditthi hi tesampi tatha samatta. ","snp4.12:5.1":"Na vahametam tathiyanti brumi, ","snp4.12:5.2":"Yamahu bala mithu annamannam; ","snp4.12:5.3":"Sakam sakam ditthimakamsu saccam, ","snp4.12:5.4":"Tasma hi baloti param dahanti”. ","snp4.12:6.1":"“Yamahu saccam tathiyanti eke, ","snp4.12:6.2":"Tamahu anne tuccham musati; ","snp4.12:6.3":"Evampi vigayha vivadayanti, ","snp4.12:6.4":"Kasma na ekam samana vadanti”. ","snp4.12:7.1":"“Ekanhi saccam na dutiyamatthi, ","snp4.12:7.2":"Yasmim paja no vivade pajanam; ","snp4.12:7.3":"Nana te saccani sayam thunanti, ","snp4.12:7.4":"Tasma na ekam samana vadanti”. ","snp4.12:8.1":"“Kasma nu saccani vadanti nana, ","snp4.12:8.2":"Pavadiyase kusalavadana; ","snp4.12:8.3":"Saccani sutani bahuni nana, ","snp4.12:8.4":"Udahu te takkamanussaranti”. ","snp4.12:9.1":"“Na heva saccani bahuni nana, ","snp4.12:9.2":"Annatra sannaya niccani loke; ","snp4.12:9.3":"Takkanca ditthisu pakappayitva, ","snp4.12:9.4":"Saccam musati dvayadhammamahu. ","snp4.12:10.1":"Ditthe sute silavate mute va, ","snp4.12:10.2":"Ete ca nissaya vimanadassi; ","snp4.12:10.3":"Vinicchaye thatva pahassamano, ","snp4.12:10.4":"Balo paro akkusaloti caha. ","snp4.12:11.1":"Yeneva baloti param dahati, ","snp4.12:11.2":"Tenatumanam kusaloti caha; ","snp4.12:11.3":"Sayamattana so kusalavadano, ","snp4.12:11.4":"Annam vimaneti tadeva pava. ","snp4.12:12.1":"Atisaraditthiya so samatto, ","snp4.12:12.2":"Manena matto paripunnamani; ","snp4.12:12.3":"Sayameva samam manasabhisitto, ","snp4.12:12.4":"Ditthi hi sa tassa tatha samatta. ","snp4.12:13.1":"Parassa ce hi vacasa nihino, ","snp4.12:13.2":"Tumo saha hoti nihinapanno; ","snp4.12:13.3":"Atha ce sayam vedagu hoti dhiro, ","snp4.12:13.4":"Na koci balo samanesu atthi. ","snp4.12:14.1":"Annam ito yabhivadanti dhammam, ","snp4.12:14.2":"Aparaddha suddhimakevali te; ","snp4.12:14.3":"Evampi titthya puthuso vadanti, ","snp4.12:14.4":"Sanditthiragena hi tebhiratta. ","snp4.12:15.1":"Idheva suddhim iti vadayanti, ","snp4.12:15.2":"Nannesu dhammesu visuddhimahu; ","snp4.12:15.3":"Evampi titthya puthuso nivittha, ","snp4.12:15.4":"Sakayane tattha dalham vadana. ","snp4.12:16.1":"Sakayane vapi dalham vadano, ","snp4.12:16.2":"Kamettha baloti param daheyya; ","snp4.12:16.3":"Sayamva so medhagamavaheyya, ","snp4.12:16.4":"Param vadam balamasuddhidhammam. ","snp4.12:17.1":"Vinicchaye thatva sayam pamaya, ","snp4.12:17.2":"Uddhamsa lokasmim vivadameti; ","snp4.12:17.3":"Hitvana sabbani vinicchayani, ","snp4.12:17.4":"Na medhagam kubbati jantu loke”ti. ","snp4.12:17.5":"Culabyuhasuttam dvadasamam. "}